org.apache.calcite.jdbc

Class CalciteRemoteDriverTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.jdbc.CalciteRemoteDriverTest

  • @NotThreadSafe
public class CalciteRemoteDriverTest
extends Object
    Test for Calcite's remote JDBC driver. Technically speaking, the test is thread safe, however Caclite/Avatica have thread-safety issues see https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CALCITE-2853.
